ould include. Would it be something for \\\"META-INF\\\"? Bootstrap might not be necessary. For another part, maybe it doesn't need to be included? Even if there are some resources, it seems that root mapping ignores non-file elements. But ultimately, I don’t think that matters too much. I should clarify my thoughts around this and see if there's a clearer point.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_23dmaVd7lNyl97CtoQ7FfWxF|fc_03b7cd5c8bd989c40169f8db7611448194a3de70df3a107641", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.squareup.okio/okio-jvm/3.0.0/src/test/kotlin/com_squareup_okio/okio_jvm/ResourceFileSystemInnerCompanionTest.kt", "edits": [{"oldText": "        override fun getResources(name: String): Enumeration<URL> {\n            requestedResourceNames += name\n            return Collections.emptyEnumeration()\n        }\n", "newText": "        override fun findResources(name: String): Enumeration<URL> {\n            requestedResourceNames += name\n            return Collections.emptyEnumeration()\n        }\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 800, "output": 1206, "cacheRead": 20480, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22486, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777916773105, "responseId": "resp_03b7cd5c8bd989c40169f8db65b6508194a714e8b224fcdd75"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_23dmaVd7lNyl97CtoQ7FfWxF|fc_03b7cd5c8bd989c40169f8db7611448194a3de70df3a107641", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in tests/src/com.squareup.okio/okio-jvm/3.0.0/src/test/kotlin/com_squareup_okio/okio_jvm/ResourceFileSystemInnerCompanionTest.kt."}], "details": {"diff": "    ...\n 27 \n 28     private class RecordingResourceClassLoader : ClassLoader(null) {\n 29         val requestedResourceNames: MutableList<String> = mutableListOf()\n 30 \n-31         ove